Our very own Senior Constable Jade from the Gold Coast now holds the Guinness World Record for most pull ups in one hour, completing 733 ðŸ’ª

Jade spent eight months training for the 24 hour record and raising money for Blue Hope, (smashing 3,500 pull ups in a 12 hour training session), but tore her bicep a week before her attempt. 

After five weeks off from doing any pull ups, she decided to tackle the one hour record. Congratulations, Jade! ðŸ’™
